data.description: Experience the perfect blend of country living and conveniences on this 37.48-acre horse property with sweeping 360-degree views, including the stunning Pikes Peak. This property boasts a 27x48 insulated Cleary shop with 220-volt power and concrete floor, an equally impressive insulated 24x55 Cleary barn, a storage shed, and a loafing shelter for your precious animals. The welcoming home features an open-concept design with a well-equipped kitchen, an adjacent dining area, that flows into the bright & open living room/great room.  The master bedroom has been smartly separated from two other bedrooms in the home, offering a more privacy. There's ample kitchen storage with the laundry/mudroom right there along with garage access add to the practicality. The entire property is securely fenced with cross-fenced pastures, mature trees, and beautiful landscaping. If you're looking for a serene and functional horse property, this is your opportunity to enjoy country living at its best.
